    "description": "Living Technologies Inc. provides real estate web services in Japan. The company operates DX platforms for various real estate services, including real estate sales, custom-built home, renovation, rental management, land utilization, and exterior wall painting. It also provides online services for real estate companies, such as real estate customer attraction navigation, SMS hunter, real estate business bank, telemarketing services for real estate appraisal, and AI real estate appraisal cloud; online business information services comprising web magazines and national real estate agency database; and online merger and acquisition intermediation and advisory services. The company was formerly known as C-STYLE Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Living Technologies Inc. in June 2018. Living Technologies Inc. was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Chuo, Japan."
